{"id":557578,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2017/04/【立此存照】为夏宝龙唱一曲只评不转的赞歌/","date":"2017-04-27T06:36:48Z","modified":"2017-04-27T06:36:48Z","title":"【立此存照】为夏宝龙唱一曲只评不转的赞歌","content":"<p><strong>【编者注】</strong>近日，一条夏宝龙卸任浙江省委书记的新闻，引来了几百条颂扬这位前省委书记的评论。然而600+的评论，却只有90条转发，这意味着绝大多数用户都只愿在评论中唱赞歌，而不是转发至自己的微博。从发表这类评论的认证用户的来看，绝大多数来自浙江各机关事业单位。</p>\n<p>有微博用户表示，这可能是由于浙江机关事业单位被下发了要求“积极评价”的任务。</p>\n<p><strong>另外，为夏宝龙唱赞歌的评论中有不少都将浙江省“三改一拆”运动作为他的政绩。该省近年来以“三改一拆”的名义<a href=\"https://theinitium.com/article/20150820-china-church-cross/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">强拆了至少1200座十字架</a>，引发了大量抗议活动，也发生过数起信徒为守护十字架而<a href=\"http://www.rfa.org/cantonese/news/religion-church-08072015090747.html\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">遭暴力对待</a>的事件。</strong></p>\n<p><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/04/夏宝龙水军1.png\"><img class=\"alignnone wp-image-557579\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/04/夏宝龙水军1.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"525\" height=\"264\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/04/夏宝龙水军1.png 1203w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/04/夏宝龙水军1-300x151.png 300w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/04/夏宝龙水军1-768x387.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/04/夏宝龙水军1-1024x516.png 1024w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 525px) 100vw, 525px\" /></a></p>\n<p><strong>以下为微博评论截图：</strong></p>\n<div id=\"attachment_557580\" style=\"width: 535px\" class=\"wp-caption alignnone\"><a href=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/04/夏宝龙水军2.png\"><img class=\"wp-image-557580\" src=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/04/夏宝龙水军2.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"525\" height=\"4368\" srcset=\"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/04/夏宝龙水军2.png 1204w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/04/夏宝龙水军2-36x300.png 36w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/04/夏宝龙水军2-768x6390.png 768w, https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/files/2017/04/夏宝龙水军2-123x1